	<p>This week&#8217;s podcast is the latest in the ongoing Three Percent Book Club. Julia Berner-Tobin of Feminist Press joins Tom and Chad to talk about Virginie Despentes&#8217;s fantastic <a href="http://www.feministpress.org/books/virginie-despentes/apocalypse-baby"><em>Apocalypse Baby</em>.</a> (And to rant about Franzen, because, of course.)</p>

